Package models

Class Contact

java.lang.Object
models.Contact
public class Contact extends Object
Contact class representing a contact record in the contact management system. Demonstrates encapsulation by keeping fields private and providing controlled access through getters and setters. This is an entity class that maps to the contacts table in the database.
Version:
1.0
Author:
CMPE-343 Project Group
